channel.title: Fresh melodic collab?
channel.description: So I know I have a bad habit of starting collabs but then going silent on them so I want to change that here. I want to start something brand new, preferably very melodic and chord oriented (I’m very inspired by Avicii btw). If that suits anyone lemme know and we can get to work!
